data.description: Welcome to this Charming 4-bedroom, 2 bath property is ideal for a family. This well maintained home located in the Rognel Heights Community is conveniently located minutes from I 695, downtown  Baltimore, and plans are in place for a Multi Million Dollar redevelopment for the Edmondson Village Shopping Center. Situated on the End of  a quiet home owner block, near amenities, schools, shops and stores.  Main level features include an open concept floor plan, gleaming hardwood floors, stainless steel appliances, quartz counter top and large island, crown molding and recessed lighting. Upper level features wall to wall carpet, 3 bedroom rooms and 1 full bathroom, lower level features, wall to wall carpet, one bedroom, family room, full bathroom and front loading washer and dryer. Don't miss the opportunity to own this property with enormous value and equity upside. Contact me today for your private tour!
